name: Michelle Greenwell
what_you_do: Michelle Greenwell has been an avid educator, creator, choreographer, director, and performer in the dance and wellness industry for over 40 years.
who_you_serve: Michelle offers online and in-person classes and programs for students of all ages and stages, from preschool to grandparenthood.
social_proof: Michelle has presented at various dance and wellness conferences, including IADMS, NDEO, Healthy Dancer Canada, ADEA, Limerick University, and more.
signature_programs: Michelle has published several themed teaching manuals, two children's books, and a CD: 'Stacey on the Keyboard' with children's musician Dan 'the Music Man' Devion.
business_focus: Providing dance and wellness programs, classes, and resources for individuals of all ages.
service_provided: dance classes, wellness programs, dance education resources
